---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Heading from '../components/sections/Heading.astro';
---

<Layout title="About the Voyage - Boating Accident" currentPage="about">
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-[#061126] text-white py-16 border-b border-gray-700 col-span-5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-left">
        <Heading level={1} size="4xl" class="sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          About
        </Heading>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-400 font-mono">
          Conference Information
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 col-span-5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-16">
        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <Heading level={2} size="3xl" class="mb-6">Our Mission</Heading>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-4 font-mono">
              Boating Accident isn't just another crypto conference—it's a maritime journey through the uncharted waters of blockchain innovation. We believe the best discoveries happen when you venture beyond safe harbors.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-mono">
              Our mission is to gather the boldest crypto navigators, from seasoned captains to eager deckhands, for an unforgettable voyage of learning, networking, and treasure hunting in the digital seas.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#061126] p-8 border border-gray-600">
            <div class="text-center">
              <Heading level={3} size="xl" class="mb-2">Adventure Awaits</Heading>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">Join us for a conference like no other, where crypto meets the high seas</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What to Expect -->
        <div>
          <Heading level={2} size="3xl" class="mb-8 text-center">What to Expect</Heading>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-[#061126] p-6 border border-gray-600 text-center">
              <Heading level={3} size="xl" class="mb-3">Expert Navigation</Heading>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">Learn from the most experienced crypto captains who've weathered many storms and discovered countless treasures.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#061126] p-6 border border-gray-600 text-center">
              <Heading level={3} size="xl" class="mb-3">Crew Networking</Heading>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">Form alliances with fellow sailors, share tales of your voyages, and plan future expeditions together.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#061126] p-6 border border-gray-600 text-center">
              <Heading level={3} size="xl" class="mb-3">Treasure Discovery</Heading>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">Uncover hidden gems in the crypto world through hands-on workshops and exclusive insights.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- History -->
        <div class="bg-[#061126] p-8 border border-gray-600">
          <Heading level={2} size="3xl" class="mb-6">The Legend</Heading>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-4 font-mono">
            The story goes that in the early days of crypto, a group of pioneering traders set sail for uncharted digital waters. What started as a simple voyage turned into an unexpected adventure—a "boating accident" that led to the discovery of incredible treasures.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-mono">
            Today, we honor that legendary journey by bringing together modern-day crypto explorers for their own adventure. Who knows what treasures you'll discover at Boating Accident 2025?
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Location -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <Heading level={2} size="3xl" class="mb-6">Port of Call</Heading>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-4 font-mono">Finland - The Land of a Thousand Lakes</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-mono">
            Our maritime adventure will dock in beautiful Finland, where the convergence of Nordic innovation and crypto culture creates the perfect harbor for our conference.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>